(Q57. Jack Welch, former CEO of GE, championed the "four E’s of leadership". What do they stand for?) Tj
ET
BT
/F1 8.5 Tf
9.7749999999999986 TL
0.196 g
56.6929133858267775 765.3545669291338527 Td
(A\) Effectiveness, Efficiency, Environment, Equity) Tj
