BT
/F1 8.5 Tf
9.7749999999999986 TL
0.196 g
297.6377952755905767 765.3545669291338527 Td
(B\) Energy, Energise, Edge, and Execution) Tj
ET
BT
/F1 8.5 Tf
9.7749999999999986 TL
0.196 g
56.6929133858267775 752.5986614173227736 Td
