BT
/F2 8 Tf
9.1999999999999993 TL
0.086 0.639 0.29 rg
56.6929133858267775 737.0081102362204319 Td
(Answer: B\) Energy, Energise, Edge, and Execution. Welch believed that a successful manager must possess great energy, spark others, have a competitive spirit, and execute plans flawlessly) Tj
