9.1999999999999993 TL
0.086 0.639 0.29 rg
56.6929133858267775 391.1813385826770855 Td
(Answer: C\) Because it deals with human beings and human behaviour. The outcomes of management experiments cannot be accurately predicted or perfectly replicated) Tj
