/F2 8 Tf
9.1999999999999993 TL
0.086 0.639 0.29 rg
56.6929133858267775 367.086850393700729 Td
(Answer: B\) No, because while associations like AIMA have a code, membership is not mandatory and has no statutory backing. Thus, there is no universal compulsion for all managers to abide by a singular statutory code) Tj
